{"tid":687342,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"拉脫維亞消防員玩命救援 空中接住跳樓男","createTime":"2018-06-02T07:31:38.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-02T07:55:20.000Z","uid":34572,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"f3b313a824ed0a23e1d3910cbeb8d6b5eca5408a","tid":687342,"uid":34572,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-02T07:31:38.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://gaus.ee/2018/06/save-jump-lit/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fgaus.ee%2F2018%2F06%2Fsave-jump-lit%2F&d=erNGLdZGAKQJnf37bPnvCI9%2BoveFa0K0Z8Wn6wXPu4k%3D&h=cdaed9a4\" target=\"_blank\">http://gaus.ee/2018/06/save-jump-lit/</a><br />\n拉脫維亞 &ndash; 當地一隊消防員，竟然達成一個難度超高嘅救援行動，竟然嘗試接住一個跳樓嘅男人。<br />\n<br />\n案情指男子企跳，但唔知消防進入佢個單位否則立即跳，消防員唯有係下一次窗口部署，一人伸出窗外，並綁好安全帶，另一人則進一步固定佢。<br />\n<br />\n最後消防員竟然可以接住跳樓男。事件搞到內務相都出黎讚揚。<br />\n<br />\n片<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/pg/Latvianfirefighters/videos/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fpg%2FLatvianfirefighters%2Fvideos%2F&d=erNGLdZGAKQJnf37bPnvCI9%2BoveFa0K0Z8Wn6wXPu4k%3D&h=0080f96c\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/pg/Latvianfirefighters/videos/</a>"},{"pid":"0f99c17d6cc7a6ee98f0ae2f1ec550a0294191ec","tid":687342,"uid":42661,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-02T07:35:22.000Z","msg":"篇文好似小學生扮記者寫咁"},{"pid":"bc8ac9b181850aa81afbb371efb903ae82184941","tid":687342,"uid":34572,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-02T07:35:45.000Z","msg":"片<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/Latvianfirefighters/videos/2200601706622336/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FLatvianfirefighters%2Fvideos%2F2200601706622336%2F&d=erNGLdZGAKQJnf37bPnvCI9%2BoveFa0K0Z8Wn6wXPu4k%3D&h=0385481c\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/Latvianfirefighters/videos/2200601706622336/</a>"},{"pid":"cfe4f8a7c99d59baec9e38a31e9703f8d0938bca","tid":687342,"uid":61882,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":